                <note rend="inline" type="source">871.51/251</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Roumanian Legation</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Department of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Memorandum</hi>
                </p>
                <p>It has come to the knowledge of the Roumanian Government that some of the gold
                    that reaches the United States at present, is part of the Roumanian gold which
                    was sent in 1916 to Moscow for safety, and is used by the Soviet Authorities to
                    make payments abroad.</p>
                <p>The Roumanian Government … considers himself obliged to formulate reservations as
                    to its final distribution.</p>
                <closer>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-08-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 15, 1921</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
